ity case sister around."],[4554,4704,"She's the girl from the lab."]],"53":[[25,133,"She's the girl from the lab,"],[133,271,"the one I paid to have blown up."],[425,504,"What?"],[621,767,"She survived."],[1130,1201,"And now she's here"],[1201,1363,"pretending to be someone else."],[1388,1514,"Clinging to Roman so"],[1514,1634,"she can get his money."],[2323,2469,"Revealing her true identity to"],[2469,2669,"Roman is gonna make my day."],[3098,3157,"Hey."],[3395,3482,"What's wrong?"],[3532,3595,"Oh,"],[3670,3803,"I think that they"],[3803,3933,"know who I really am."]],"54":[[25,141,"I think that they"],[141,250,"know who I really am."],[575,642,"Here."],[1372,1484,"Hey, are you sure?"],[1580,1680,"I don't know, I just..."],[1843,1906,"I have this kind of"],[1906,2031,"funny feeling about it."],[2160,2260,"Okay, well hey"],[2260,2369,"I don't want you to worry."],[2519,2623,"So if they do find out"],[2623,2769,"and tell my father, then,"],[2869,2952,"I'll take the blame."],[2952,3019,"What?"],[3019,3073,"Alright."],[3194,3215,"Hey,"],[3336,3440,"I'll protect you."],[3516,3561,"No."],[3741,3924,"No, we're in this together, okay?"],[3924,4074,"This was practically my idea."],[4270,4450,"Okay, well, then maybe we just go"],[4450,4583,"back inside and tell the truth."],[4775,4838,"And,"],[5000,5100,"maybe it's,"],[5180,5255,"maybe it's time we"],[5255,5334,"stop pretending,"],[5518,5726,"that we're just friends."],[5955,6056,"Roman..."],[6151,6343,"You don't mean that."],[8308,8416,"I do."],[8925,8975,"We can't,"],[9042,9292,"we can't do this, okay? We are,"],[9292,9551,"we are from two completely"],[9551,9684,"different worlds."],[9909,9989,"Your family might"],[9989,10222,"eventually accept Emily, but,"],[10360,10556,"they'll never accept me."],[10764,10810,"Then,"],[10856,10915,"then tell me."],[11048,11240,"Tell me you don't want this."]],"55":[[350,383,"They'll never"],[383,500,"accept me for who I am."],[633,809,"I'm a doctor who has"],[809,955,"been studying and working"],[955,1076,"for years trying to find"],[1076,1305,"a cure with no success."],[1555,1647,"I'm a nobody."],[1718,1776,"No,"],[1839,2089,"no, you are so much more."],[2168,2360,"And I will do everything"],[2477,2644,"to make sure my family sees that."],[3641,3728,"Come on."],[3807,3924,"Let's go back."],[3970,4066,"Okay."],[4771,4938,"I saw her with Roman,"],[4954,5038,"at the clinic,"],[5313,5397,"with the sick girl."],[5476,5572,"So I wasn't wrong?"],[5718,5922,"That's her, the girl from the lab."],[5964,6097,"Jennifer Connor."],[6181,6302,"Not Emily."],[6389,6523,"Not one of us."],[6594,6819,"And completely disposable."],[6894,6981,"Bill already thinks"],[6981,7061,"that Jennifer Connor"],[7061,7186,"is complete a failure."],[7311,7399,"It's gonna be so"],[7399,7545,"easy to get rid of her."],[8483,8679,"Tonight the Johnson family hosts"],[8679,8854,"the Grand Gala dinner."],[9008,9225,"The press, investors,"],[9267,9476,"and society's finest."],[9517,9713,"A night for legacy,"],[9797,9959,"and for truth."],[10514,10764,"And tonight she falls."],[11077,11261,"No one's going to ruin this night."],[11749,11849,"We're in this together."],[12166,12324,"And very soon,"],[12374,12454,"the world will know"],[12454,12600,"exactly who you are."]],"56":[[996,1055,"Hey."],[1251,1317,"You know,"],[1401,1559,"it truly amazes me."],[1655,1714,"What?"],[1818,1897,"How you always seem to"],[1897,2022,"take my breath away."],[4379,4479,"Roman,"],[4517,4658,"Johnson Global has doubled"],[4658,4779,"profits under your lead."],[4804,4900,"How do you explain it?"],[4950,5013,"Simple."],[5096,5234,"I don't follow trends."],[5267,5351,"I set them."],[5680,5751,"And tonight,"],[5797,5980,"is this your biggest investment yet?"],[6072,6214,"She's not an investment."],[6235,6368,"Emily is pure gold."],[6869,7019,"Tonight, the Johnson legacy"],[7019,7244,"celebrates not just our"],[7244,7394,"fortune, but our future."],[7607,7887,"My son, Roman, and his bride-to-be,"],[7887,8028,"Miss Emily Walker."],[8579,8646,"See?"],[8700,8904,"I told you my father would love you."],[9693,9843,"Make sure the world sees this"],[9843,9984,"before the night is through."]],"57":[[12,225,"Tonight the Johnson family honors"],[225,458,"not just our legacy, but our future"],[458,638,"with Roman and Emily."],[1317,1422,"I just can't take"],[1422,1659,"my eyes off you, Jen."],[2665,2902,"This family was built on strength,"],[2948,3165,"vision, and risk."],[3315,3586,"Everything I built, my deals and companies,"],[3712,3853,"came from knowing when to"],[3928,4200,"stand by my choices,"],[4279,4517,"which is why marrying Emily"],[4704,4984,"is the easiest choice I've ever made."],[5334,5480,"She won't survive what's coming."],[5647,5689,"End her."],[5834,5897,"Now."],[6018,6151,"I have it on good authority that"],[6151,6293,"she's been faking her identity."],[7465,7549,"It's true,"],[7628,7716,"Roman,"],[7766,7891,"It's time you learned who"],[7891,8087,"your fiancée really is."]],"58":[[12,129,"She's a fraud."],[262,417,"Her name isn't Emily Walker."],[462,563,"It's Jennifer Connor."],[1501,1655,"Jennifer Connor?"],[1764,1976,"That rebellious doctor who's been"],[1976,2068,"trying to work on"],[2068,2248,"a cure for her sister?"],[2610,2790,"No. No, it can't be."],[2965,3073,"That's right."],[3136,3328,"She's been lying to you, Roman,"],[3382,3478,"To all of you!"],[3858,3945,"Here's the proof."],[4099,4421,"Same woman, same fraud."],[5159,5276,"Enough!"],[5668,5905,"All right, it's true, everything."],[6239,6327,"All of it."],[6777,6940,"But what you don't know is why."],[7165,7265,"She did it for love,"],[7444,7632,"for her sister, for me"],[7778,7982,"not for money or power."],[8450,8579,"You knew?"],[8612,8725,"Of course."],[8879,9038,"Because unlike you,"],[9113,9267,"I know what's in her heart."],[9672,9855,"I love her for who she is,"],[9926,10155,"and not what's in her bank account."],[10155,10285,"I want her,"],[10372,10481,"not for show."],[10548,10652,"And not for the good of the family,"],[10652,10777,"but because I love her."],[11982,12078,"Do you,"],[12203,12324,"do you really mean that?"]],"59":[[25,258,"Well, if she truly belongs here,"],[383,529,"then let her prove it."],[604,750,"But not with money,"],[842,1138,"and not with status, but with words."],[1222,1301,"Come,"],[1451,1555,"speak,"],[1593,1860,"and convince all these people here"],[1935,2064,"why you deserve to"],[2064,2256,"stand next to my son."],[2494,2665,"And why I shouldn't have you thrown"],[2665,2957,"in jail for identity fraud?"],[3157,3211,"Hey,"],[3261,3349,"you can do this."],[3415,3620,"Alright, just speak from your heat."],[5789,5993,"I wasn't born into"],[5993,6218,"wealth or legacy."],[6368,6581,"I don't know the games that you play or"],[6660,6827,"rules that you make for yourselves."],[7002,7152,"But I know sacrifice."],[7290,7474,"I know what it means to fight for"],[7474,7674,"your family and give everything you"],[7674,7824,"have for your loved ones."],[7920,7987,"And that's why I'm"],[7987,8078,"standing here today."],[8128,8299,"It's not about a name."],[8379,8591,"It's about loyalty and"],[8666,8762,"and love."],[9092,9501,"So, judge me if you want."],[9680,9784,"Call me a fraud."],[9943,10068,"But don't you dare"],[10089,10268,"say that I don't belong."],[10427,10664,"Because I would walk through fire"],[10664,10802,"for the people that I love."],[10981,11148,"And I won't apologize for that."],[11373,11473,"Jen."]],"60":[[1176,1305,"Please say something."],[1334,1426,"End this."],[1601,1722,"Impressive."],[1868,2093,"Strength under fire."],[2377,2540,"Now that's what a"],[2540,2748,"Johnson wife needs to have."],[3073,3232,"From this night forward,"],[3232,3403,"the Johnson name will"],[3403,3578,"back all of your work."],[3866,4112,"And I am hereby reinstating all funding"],[4112,4270,"for your sister's treatment."],[5000,5084,"You know,"],[5159,5330,"I can tell you're not pretending."],[5572,5689,"You know this is real."],[6131,6177,"Real?"],[6473,6610,"Oh my God."]],"61":[[1564,1680,"You know, I,"],[1885,2085,"I truly meant what I said out there."],[2648,2811,"And I can't wait any longer to tell you"],[2811,3040,"how I really feel."],[3257,3315,"Jen,"],[3595,3724,"I love you."],[4879,4954,"Will you,"],[5134,5267,"will you actually marry me?"],[5534,5576,"Yes."],[8616,8729,"She's gone."]],"62":[[604,696,"Good morning."],[738,867,"My soon-to-be wife."],[1063,1184,"Doctor Connor, Mr. Johnson,"],[1184,1272,"it's Mia."],[1272,1422,"You have to come, now."],[2056,2114,"Mia."],[3591,3737,"Family before fraud."],[3787,3941,"If you want your sister alive,"],[4116,4241,"leave Roman forever."],[4325,4383,"No."],[4421,4525,"They've taken her."],[4579,4642,"No."],[4725,4884,"They don't get to decide this."],[5046,5167,"We're going to get her back,"],[5230,5284,"together."],[5359,5417,"Okay?"]],"63":[[41,171,"They want me to give him up."],[287,529,"Lose Roman or lose her."],[600,709,"What do I do?"],[800,1051,"It's Kim and Genevieve. It has to be."],[1155,1226,"Listen to me."],[1376,1505,"You are not alone."],[1676,1872,"We are going to get your sister back."],[2085,2147,"Okay."],[2252,2318,"Come on."],[2652,2736,"Pull up every recording"],[2736,2882,"from the last hour, now."],[3174,3311,"Wait. Wait. That's her."],[3395,3507,"She's the one that helped them."],[3641,3678,"Wait."],[3837,3941,"Zoom in right there."],[4341,4441,"That's from the estate."],[4512,4646,"They couldn't have taken her far."],[4654,4742,"Well, that means that they're still"],[4742,4871,"here on the estate grounds."],[5075,5159,"The East Wing."],[5159,5276,"It's been sealed off for years."],[5301,5372,"They have to be there."],[5372,5459,"Come on. Let's go."]],"64":[[608,650,"Mia!"],[671,704,"Wait."],[796,950,"Wrong move, lady."],[1000,1092,"Hey, stay back."],[2519,2577,"Come on."],[2748,2806,"Mia."],[2923,3044,"Mia, come on."],[3182,3274,"Move, move."],[4137,4195,"Roman, stop,"],[4195,4275,"you're gonna hurt yourself."],[4396,4496,"Better me than her."]],"65":[[0,200,"Mia, hey, hey."],[291,513,"Oh, hey."],[575,667,"It's okay."],[667,779,"I told you I'd protect her."],[779,838,"I know."],[917,1092,"Thank you. You did."],[1501,1726,"Oh, touching."],[2256,2348,"Truly."],[2510,2602,"But who's going to believe you"],[2602,2719,"when you say we took her?"],[2811,3053,"We'll still be at Bill's table long"],[3053,3215,"after you're gone."],[3274,3370,"We're new Johnsons."],[3428,3678,"And one day, all of this will be ours."],[3778,3887,"You kidnapped her,"],[4003,4104,"and almost killed her."],[4254,4500,"I'll make sure you rot before I let you"],[4500,4642,"harm this family again."],[4884,5146,"You can't win, Emily."],[5230,5288,"Or,"],[5330,5372,"Jennifer."],[5372,5480,"Whatever you call yourself."],[5605,5780,"Sooner or later, we'll bury you."],[5947,6014,"They're right."],[6101,6243,"How am I ever going to feel safe if"],[6243,6364,"they keep coming after me?"],[7098,7294,"So, it was you?"]],"66":[[70,141,"Bill!"],[254,346,"This isn't what it looks like."],[362,454,"Silence!"],[688,863,"I heard everything!"],[913,1134,"You kidnapped that child?"],[1630,1876,"You endangered this family's life."],[1968,2056,"Baby."],[2143,2231,"Baby."],[2302,2448,"You know that we are"],[2448,2623,"meant to be together."],[2844,2982,"Don't let her poison"],[2982,3178,"your mind against me."],[3470,3628,"You dare."],[3741,4045,"You conspired against my own blood?"],[4154,4437,"You are no wife of mine."],[4537,4750,"We only wanted to protect the fortune."],[4792,4896,"Everything we did..."],[4896,5055,"Everything you did brought shame to"],[5055,5180,"this family's name."],[5413,5530,"Get rid of these two."],[5618,5672,"No."],[5697,5751,"No."],[6185,6306,"Bill, you can't do this!"],[6819,6919,"You'll never last."],[6969,7132,"You will never be one of us!"],[7190,7315,"Not one of you?"],[7424,7611,"Maybe that's one of my strengths."],[7670,7920,"No! No! No!"],[7920,8045,"No! Let go!"],[8537,8608,"You,"],[8758,8867,"you exposed them."],[9129,9263,"And if it wasn't for you,"],[9426,9513,"I'd still be sleeping"],[9513,9676,"with a snake in my bed!"],[9788,9851,"Me?"],[9930,10164,"He's, thanking me?"],[10218,10456,"They were never a part of this family."],[10714,10777,"Jen..."],[10877,10960,"She's more than"],[10960,11140,"proven that she's worthy."],[11223,11394,"You saved her life,"],[11628,11757,"and mine."]],"67":[[421,596,"Mia, hey it's me."],[884,1071,"It's me. You gotta wake up, okay?"],[1309,1393,"I,"],[1438,1580,"I changed my name."],[1647,1839,"I've been pretending to be one of them."],[1893,2085,"I've been playing all of their games."],[2181,2289,"I did it for you."],[2310,2477,"Okay, I did it all for you so you gotta"],[2477,2631,"wake up for me please."],[2723,2831,"Come on Mia."],[2902,3178,"Please. I gave up everything."],[3478,3645,"I gave up my pride and my,"],[3687,3887,"my heart and my soul for you."],[4458,4633,"Just so you could stay alive."],[4775,4867,"Please."],[4946,5134,"Mia, please you gotta wake up."],[5818,5955,"Mia, please."],[6022,6222,"Come back. I need you"],[6222,6381,"I really need you."],[6990,7086,"Mia."],[7828,7899,"Jen."],[8204,8312,"Roman,"],[8525,8708,"there's something that I need to tell you."],[8804,8938,"What is it?"],[9159,9292,"I can't be with you."]],"68":[[29,108,"Say it again."],[329,471,"No, I want you to look me in the eyes"],[471,700,"and tell me you don't love me."],[850,1026,"I lied to your family, Roman."],[1076,1172,"I played their games"],[1172,1418,"and I wore their dresses."],[1505,1901,"Everything about Emily was just fake."],[2001,2268,"You deserve so much better."],[2268,2585,"You deserve more than just a fraud."],[2765,2831,"Better?"],[3040,3165,"Better, Jen?"],[3336,3611,"I've spent my entire life surrounded by"],[3611,3853,"polished liars. I don't want better."],[4008,4166,"I want real and you were the only real"],[4166,4333,"thing that I've ever had in my life."],[4383,4692,"Why is he fighting for me after all the"],[4692,4792,"masks I wore?"],[4833,4963,"All the lies I told?"],[5059,5284,"You risked everything for Mia."],[5284,5434,"You risked yourself for me."],[5434,5672,"That's not fraud, Jen."],[5672,5797,"That's love."],[5960,6018,"But I..."],[6018,6160,"No, listen to me."],[6335,6644,"You're mine not because of a name"],[6644,6802,"or because of a fortune,"],[6848,6973,"but because I love you."],[7119,7453,"And I will fight every day for the rest"],[7453,7653,"of my life for you if I have to."],[7912,8024,"So tell me now,"],[8133,8295,"is your heart mine or not?"]],"69":[[0,154,"Is your heart mine or not?"],[538,583,"Yes."],[779,967,"It always has been."],[1559,1634,"Come here."],[2435,2552,"Took you long enough."],[2777,2836,"Mia."],[3023,3144,"Mia you're awake."],[3591,3674,"You're awake."],[3674,3849,"She's cured."],[3849,4200,"My heart, my family, my future."],[4312,4421,"You did it. I knew"],[4421,4558,"you would find the cure."],[4800,4900,"We did it."]],"70":[[54,237,"For once, this house doesn't feel like"],[237,342,"a cage."],[358,592,"It feels like a promise."],[771,930,"Still doubting you look like a bride?"],[1380,1589,"You always said love was dangerous."],[1589,1689,"I guess you were right."],[1776,1876,"But it's worth it."],[2043,2302,"You saved me. He saved you."],[2506,2556,"I guess that's what"],[2556,2698,"happy endings look like."],[2898,2969,"You know, you're supposed to be"],[2969,3086,"the little sister, right?"],[3199,3370,"Why do you sound wiser than me?"],[3486,3653,"Because you taught me how to fight."],[3720,3878,"Now it's your turn to live."],[4904,5017,"You're,"],[5067,5221,"sure about this,"],[5255,5397,"after everything that's happened?"],[5501,5834,"She's faced fire, lies, and even you."],[5910,6122,"More than anyone else in our family has."],[6168,6314,"Yet she's still standing."],[6327,6398,"Yeah."],[6556,6652,"Well, you know,"],[6748,6940,"she's a Johnson then."],[7023,7232,"In every way that matters."],[7315,7482,"All the best to you, okay."],[7557,7665,"I love you, buddy."],[7782,7907,"Take care, okay?"],[8758,8975,"Once wearing a dress this elegant"],[8975,9113,"would have been disguise."],[9159,9401,"Now, it's who I am."],[9976,10147,"God, she's really here."],[10197,10335,"My wife."]],"71":[[133,362,"Once I hid behind a fake name."],[429,492,"Now,"],[583,813,"I finally want to be seen."],[1272,1359,"You're late."],[1518,1676,"You know, you really had me sweating."],[1730,1897,"Had to make sure you're worth it first."],[2081,2198,"Roman Johnson,"],[2227,2431,"do you take Jennifer Connor?"],[2431,2506,"I do,"],[2565,2631,"and I will,"],[2706,2898,"every day for the rest of our lives."],[3186,3432,"You taught me what real love is."],[3432,3707,"It's not about wealth or power."],[3707,3795,"It's about this."],[3895,3958,"You."],[4066,4141,"Us."],[4554,4750,"Then by the power vested in me..."],[4900,4996,"Took you long enough."],[5759,5855,"I'm yours,"],[5947,6010,"forever."],[6072,6331,"I came here with nothing but lies."],[6360,6460,"And somehow,"],[6489,6698,"I found everything real."]]}